Dsdata ProductPrint is a solution to print catalog product pages direct from the Magento store frontend.
If enabled in the backend it shows some print links on the product pages to print in different versions.

- Print PopUp
- Direct Print
- *Create PDF

ToDo:
- *Implement the PDF creation on the fly as the third of 3 links
- *Search for a way to use Zend_Pdf comonent and fill the pdf file with dynamic product data

Demo URL: http://www.dsdata.de/magedev/sony-vaio-vgn-txn27n-b-11-1-notebook-pc.html


